body:
@yekeren @gauss-clb 
I met the same problem but mine crashes when [a default saver is created](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/contrib/slim/python/slim/learning.py#L658)
 inside slim.learning.train for it requires all variables in the graph to be found in the checkpoint. If an explicit saver is defined using var_list, newly inserted variables won't be tracked and saved later on. May I know how did you work this out? Thanks!
